\begin_layout Subsection
Rules
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Risk is a turn-based for two to six players.
 In the standard Risk Game, Earth has six continents and 42 regions.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Graphics
